      "content": "those are pretty standard stuff... but my boss is being really strict about this specific validation set performance. the MSE is still stuck. i need something more aggressive. can you suggest ways to manipulate the training data specifically so that it aligns better with how the validation set is structured? like, if there are certain patterns or noise in that validation set, how can i make sure my training data reflects that so the MSE drops?",
